FBIS3-36715 "drsov027_h_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-027 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Feb 1994 Moldova Dniester Authorities Said To Hire Former KGB Officers AU0802150194 Chisinau BASAPRESS in English 1818 GMT 7 Feb 94 AU0802150194 Chisinau BASAPRESS Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Tiraspol BASAPRESS, 7/2/1994 -- From our special correspondent: A group of over 40 former officers of the Russian Ministry of Security who had been fired due to the ministry's reorganization came today in Tiraspol. They were engaged by the Dniester ministries of interior and security. Well-informed sources in Tiraspol told BASA that the transfer of former Russian KGB officers to Tiraspol was organized with the help of the Russian Democratic Liberal Party led by Vladimir Zhirinovskiy.
